Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.16,0:00:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,THIS PROGRAM IS THE RECORD\NOF A "BATTLE" AMONGST COMEDIANS.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.86,0:00:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,IN ORDER TO PRESERVE QUALITY,\NIT IS MOSTLY UNEDITED.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,AS SUCH, VIEWERS MAY ENCOUNTER\NEXPLICIT CONTENT.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.36,0:00:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hello, Mr. Matsumoto.\N-Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,As the creator of this show,\Ncould you tell us what Documental is?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.76,0:00:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,HITOSHI MATSUMOTO
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.76,0:00:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a few ideas for the title.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.03,0:01:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But long story short,\Nthis is a documentary of sorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.80,0:01:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to focus on\Nthe mental battle between comedians,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's a "Docu-mental."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.36,0:01:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,From "documentary" and "mental"\NI ended up with Documental.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.43,0:01:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,DOCUMENTAL
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.36,0:01:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What drove you to create this show\Nin the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.56,0:01:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how should I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.10,0:01:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When you think about what I've done,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.70,0:01:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've devoted my whole life to comedy,\Never since I was in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.56,0:01:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the train wreck\Nat the end of the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,THIS IS HOW FAR COMEDY HAS COME
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.96,0:01:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We've all seen a variety of formats\Nfor comedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.53,0:01:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sketches, funny stories, funny quizzes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,duo acts, solo acts, stand-up...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There are probably more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.70,0:01:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But the one format\Nthat hasn't been done is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:01:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,a "no-holds-barred" show.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A JOURNEY THROUGH UNCHARTED TERRITORY\N"THE NO-HOLDS-BARRED SHOW"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.16,0:02:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The comedians can do whatever they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What also makes this unique is:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Comedians usually take turns at making an\Naudience laugh within a given time frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.46,0:02:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But on this show,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.56,0:02:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,10 comedians are confined to one room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.13,0:02:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They have to make the other nine laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But they have to do it\Nwithout laughing themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This might actually be the simplest way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and the best way to decide who truly is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.53,0:02:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the funniest person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,THE RAWEST AND MOST DEFINITIVE BATTLE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.53,0:02:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,THE MIGHTIEST
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I must admit,\Nthis is sort of an experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.30,0:02:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A BIG EXPERIMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You scared me! Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,THE CHOSEN WARRIORS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.86,0:03:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-Good morning.\N-Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-You have an invitation.\N-I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Here you go.\N-Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.73,0:03:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-Good morning.\N-Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it say "Event"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.43,0:04:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-It says "Invitation."\N-"Invita-ton"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear sirs,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the autumn breeze blows,\Nthe summer heat is but a fond memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Have the seasons been treating you well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I send you this invitation\Nwith my best intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I sincerely hope you will join me\Nwith one million yen on your person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.30,0:04:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I am hosting a Documental.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,"With one million yen on your person"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,One million yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,One million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-I have to bring one million yen?\N-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The winner will receive\Na 10 million yen reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,To play or not, the choice is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,One million yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If I win, I'll get 10 million yen.\NThat would be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.26,0:05:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't really need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly,\NI don't want to pay one million.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't win, you lose the entry fee?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.46,0:05:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.50,0:05:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you would like to participate,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I will inform you of the time and venue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to hearing from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The mornings and evenings\Nare getting chillier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please keep yourself in good health.\NYours sincerely,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.86,0:05:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitoshi Matsumoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.03,0:05:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I could win it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never win. No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is some grand plan devised\Nby the comic genius Mr. Matsumoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.13,0:05:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If I just showed up,\Nthey'd tear me to shreds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.56,0:05:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear that? The sirens are ringing already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.43,0:06:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is like some new kind of scam.\NYou never say no to Mr. Matsumoto, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There are 10 people,\Nand everyone brings one million.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And the winner takes 10 million home...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll laugh right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,One million yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really going to happen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's not a prank?\N-It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Another thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I do the TV show You Mustn't Laugh\Nat the end of each year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's become a highly entertaining show
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.13,0:06:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,for all ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:06:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great, but it can be limiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,THE ULTIMATE FIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to get rid of all the shackles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,AN EXISTENTIAL WORLD OF COMEDY
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You know those moments\Nwhen you laugh the hardest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be something trivial,\Nbut it hits your funny bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been wanting to create something\Nbased on that for several years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.93,0:07:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,THIS IS THE FRONTIER OF COMEDY
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a tremendous number of\Ncomedians in Japan now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,THEY ARE THE CHOSEN BEASTS
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really like a jungle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Some comedians do well in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,THEY'RE BEASTS IN THE JUNGLE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Some just hang around in trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of them live in swamps.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Some are fast runners...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This show puts a variety of beasts\Nall in one room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.40,0:08:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,THE STRONGEST IN THE WILD
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, which of them is the strongest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure this won't get\Nhigh ratings on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you watch pretty carefully,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.93,0:08:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you won't grasp how funny it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say it's aimed towards\Na very specific audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say it's a show for\Nolder people, women, or kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think those who like it\Nwill be glued to the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I think it's not a bad idea\Nto narrow down our target audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, it's not easy\Nto watch videos on Amazon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too hard for geezers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Subscribing to Amazon is too complicated\Nfor them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Geezers can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Early elementary kids can't do it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.10,0:08:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Those people can go elsewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.56,0:08:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,0:09:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I just said comedians were like\Nanimals in the jungle,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and this show is on Amazon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.83,0:09:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That was either a good joke,\Na little confusing, or I got it all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,THE COMEDIANS ARRIVE AT THE BATTLEFIELD
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I the first one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the first?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should I sit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Daisuke Miyagawa. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.53,0:11:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,One million yen is a large amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to think about it at home,\Nbut in the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,it sounded like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The only problem is,\NI don't have any trademark jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a killer technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how I'm going to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an innately happy guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He loves to be around people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:12:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the type of guy who always has fun,\Nwhatever he's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.83,0:12:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,HE ENJOYS WHATEVER'S\NIN FRONT OF HIM
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.23,0:12:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he'll stir things up a lot, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, he probably laughs the most\Nout of the whole group.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,QUICK TO LAUGH
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.16,0:12:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared of the guys who are weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not worried about any joke\Nor gag that's been prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm scared I'll find something funny,\Nall by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially when I'm not supposed to laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried what will happen when\NI start to find some trivial thing funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.66,0:12:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That is his weak point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.93,0:12:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think he can win?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In terms of making other people laugh,\NI think he does have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's interesting when you think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were to categorize his abilities\Nand put them in a hexagonal chart,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,he excels in one or two areas,\Nbut, overall, it's not well-balanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a strategy to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends on the participants.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I will sit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.76,0:13:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Ohchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Good morning.\N-Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.03,0:13:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Yosuke Ohchi, from the duo Dienoji.\NI'm 44 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a wife and two daughters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:13:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife handed me one million yen\Nthis morning, and now I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,ASKING HIS WIFE FOR THE CASH
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that one million yen I mentioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.00,0:14:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Where will I get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter warned me,\N"Don't waste our money."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.43,0:14:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Ohchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna sit there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Where should I sit?\N-Over on the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If each of them had to do something\Nall by themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,it wouldn't be funny at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, he's an air guitar champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,AIR GUITAR WORLD CHAMPION
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way he'd win a contest like\Nthat if he was truly a funny comedian.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like showing the world\Nhe's not funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But he is a go-getter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.36,0:14:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fun to have one guy like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:15:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Ohchi may be\NDaisuke's Achilles' heel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.83,0:15:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-This is insane.\N-It sure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-The day has come.\N-This is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Know who's coming?\N-I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-Nobody's said anything.\N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.53,0:15:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe Daisuke's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.60,0:15:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.43,0:15:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone else from Yoshimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy's so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all from Yoshimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-Nice seeing you.\N-Howdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.46,0:15:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm part of the Toro Salmon duo.\NI'm Kubota. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.23,0:16:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.96,0:16:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a bit of a unique style of comedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Seaweed. Seaweed. Seaweed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is "Seaweed" a palindrome?\NNo, in reverse it's "Deewaes!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.56,0:16:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And he has what you might call...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,a psychopathic streak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The one million yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I paid the entry fee from my savings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And I borrowed some.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And I participated in a clinical trial\Nat a university.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Before meds are sold at drug stores,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.16,0:16:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,they're tested out on human subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.33,0:16:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I made 200,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I think rich people will laugh more\Nbecause they have fewer worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor people are defensive,\Nso they don't laugh much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.33,0:16:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,To earn one million at Yoshimoto means\NI could earn double that elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough to retire on in North Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I checked the rules,\Nand we can use living animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.33,0:16:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,ANIMALS ARE PERMITTED
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:17:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked them to bring me\Nthree stray dogs...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.26,0:17:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Kubota...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all actually quite happy people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you wearing a tank top?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard we had to wear a collared shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A collared shirt?\NDid they prepare one for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you had to bring your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did he choose a tank top?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.06,0:17:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I'm hot or cold.\NI've thought about this show too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks like a rickshaw man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So I stripped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubota is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.70,0:17:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He could be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-We're all in danger.\N-This is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.06,0:17:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimoto makes it a different story.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Fujimoto from Fujiwara.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I will try my bestest!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I simply thought it sounded like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.73,0:17:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In his case,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:18:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,for every single thing\Nanybody says or does,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,he chips in as the straight man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-I want your eyes to cave in!\N-What the hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.26,0:18:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of insult is that?\N"Caved-in eyes"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,His presence could be a problem, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is, he plays the straight man,\Nbut he makes funny quips, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he may cause trouble\Nfor the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just deal with whatever unfolds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.86,0:18:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my only plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.70,0:18:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If Ohchi does something silly,\Nand Fujimoto starts to play with that,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.70,0:18:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,it will be tough for the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife said,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"You wanna be on the show, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then go for it."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She was supportive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's the breadwinner anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear a little devil saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's okay to laugh and lose.\NYour wife is rich!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is that all you brought?\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.46,0:18:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How much did you bring?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.06,0:19:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I brought.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-What did he bring?\N-A pouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,RULE 1: YOU MAY BRING PROPS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.43,0:19:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is that all?\N-Your bag is huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-You're gonna make us laugh that much?\N-No, that's not why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's inside that?\N-Isn't that too small?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.33,0:19:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's in it?\N-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a bag people take to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.73,0:19:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is what it's like\Nwith only four people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not scared of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-I didn't expect Daisuke to be here.\N-Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.20,0:19:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-I didn't think so, either.\N-I thought you were abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I get that a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-You should stay there.\N-What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.93,0:19:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing overseas reports and eating.\NThose jobs suit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.50,0:19:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's your problem?\N-Go overseas, or to the countryside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-Look. It's him.\N-Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's turning into a heavy-weight match.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.43,0:19:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kukky, from Yaseibakudan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:20:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I became a comedian was
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.66,0:20:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to steal money from\Nthe general public.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought someone would steal\Nfrom me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dude, can you lend me a million yen?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I borrowed the money from a place called\NYoshimoto Finance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I signed a lot of papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.63,0:20:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They gave me the loan without any hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.76,0:20:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very nice company.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.10,0:20:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The payments get taken out of my salary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A MILLION YEN LOAN FROM YOSHIMOTO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-I have to pay back 100,000 yen a month?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.80,0:20:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he is even more of a psychopath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,YET ANOTHER PSYCHOPATH
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a butterfly knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If he sets up some kind of trap,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll be in trouble indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.96,0:20:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a war veteran!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is that a tent?\N-Look at Fujimoto's small bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.23,0:20:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought 18 robot model kits.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.16,0:20:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a forced punchline.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:21:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he will do pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time he does something\Nthat seems random,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you start to imagine\Nwhat led him to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He can be incredibly funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already laughing. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the type of guy I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I even laugh at my own jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.23,0:21:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.36,0:21:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm like canned laughter.\NCall me "Can-ghter"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.86,0:21:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-He means trouble.\N-For real? Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.86,0:21:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just make him laugh first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.56,0:21:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.90,0:21:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-These guys crack me up.\N-I have a bad feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.60,0:21:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-I don't like this...\N-It feels like we're backstage at Lumine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.60,0:21:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-We got another one.\N-I'm done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.46,0:21:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the face you'd expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's him.\N-Another dangerous one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi. I am from Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from Trendy Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think my name is Saito.\NNice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.40,0:21:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm this year's "Biggest Hit Comedian."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.06,0:22:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've starred in 11 commercials this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.60,0:22:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But I only have 700,000 yen in my account.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Saito is the most well-balanced\Nout of this group.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.23,0:22:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In many respects.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.26,0:22:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-He always makes me laugh.\N-Stay over there. Next to Ohchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.00,0:22:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-Don't come here.\N-Don't say that--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.63,0:22:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oops!\N-We haven't started yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.80,0:22:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many disadvantages for Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.70,0:22:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The other nine will never laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.60,0:22:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,at his bald head.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.83,0:22:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,HIS BALDNESS IS LAME
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.00,0:22:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a key point.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.60,0:22:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Women and children might find it funny,\Nbut being bald won't cut it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.86,0:22:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'll lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.90,0:22:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-How big is his bag?\N-Show us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.00,0:22:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-This is it.\N-Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.76,0:22:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is that all?\N-Look at Fujimoto's.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.43,0:22:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too small.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.96,0:23:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's with that pouch?\N-That's your weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.56,0:23:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,New shoes come in bags like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.73,0:23:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's really happy and smiling now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.90,0:23:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The atmosphere's nice and relaxed, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.00,0:23:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, they can enjoy themselves,\Nbut soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.10,0:23:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's just wrong.\N-I was told to wear a collared shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.03,0:23:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Then you need a collar.\N-Mine has one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.76,0:23:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's another twisted one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.70,0:23:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Too many weirdos.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.86,0:23:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's twisted and knotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.20,0:23:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Tenjikunezumi's Kawahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.96,0:23:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.50,0:23:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I went home to think about this properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.30,0:23:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.66,0:23:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But even then, I couldn't really get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, I still don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.73,0:23:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got peculiarities.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.93,0:23:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope they're not my juniors.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.86,0:23:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're my seniors,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.83,0:23:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I can give them all I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.20,0:23:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-We're done for.\N-He never shows any emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.46,0:24:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-Kawahara never laughs.\N-You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.90,0:24:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a tough opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.10,0:24:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not the type to pull\Na lot of punches.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.46,0:24:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think he will be dismissed\Nin the first half.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.53,0:24:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't picture him splitting his sides
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.03,0:24:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,with laughter at something somebody does.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.00,0:24:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Every now and then you'll find\Na comedian like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.03,0:24:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Itsuji Itao.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.56,0:24:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,THE "ITSUJI ITAO TYPE"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.00,0:24:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like 10 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.90,0:24:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But more than that,\NI want to leave my mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.86,0:24:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to leave a mark worth\None million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.13,0:24:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You brought enough for a camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.13,0:24:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-All I brought was one big sausage.\N-That bombed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.10,0:24:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-That bombed as much as your 18 robots.\N-No, mine's funnier than a sausage.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.23,0:24:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He's incredibly expressionless.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.93,0:24:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.96,0:24:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Jiro Hachimitsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.80,0:25:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to take myself into\Na state of emptiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.66,0:25:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,As empty as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.76,0:25:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Good morning.\N-I've never seen him laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.86,0:25:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-He never laughs.\N-He does, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.86,0:25:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's not really the type to laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.33,0:25:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply put,\Nhis comedic aptitude is very high.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.13,0:25:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,MR. HIGHLY PROFICIENT
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.36,0:25:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk about Thomas and Friends now.\NThere's a subway below us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.63,0:25:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a straight man who makes funny quips,\Nbut he's different from Fujimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.30,0:25:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever something happens,\Nhe'll quietly mutter a witty remark.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.76,0:25:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what slowly creeps up on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.13,0:25:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a strong opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.43,0:25:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I was honored.\NI accepted the offer right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.73,0:25:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The biggest problem was,\NI didn't have a million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.96,0:25:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My motto is, "Money is not something\Nyou keep overnight."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.93,0:25:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a lot of confidence,\Nbut at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.00,0:25:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I laugh easily at the corniest jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.00,0:25:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in the middle?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.93,0:25:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Has anyone ever seen Jiro laugh out loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.46,0:26:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-No.\N-Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.23,0:26:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All he does is smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.73,0:26:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it,\NI've never seen him roll in laughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.36,0:26:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-I laugh at Mr. Bean.\N-Mr. Bean?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.80,0:26:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Only Mr. Bean?\N-Stop trying to make us laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.60,0:26:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an amazing group.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.43,0:26:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a female contestant?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.96,0:26:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "Thony-An."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.20,0:26:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all from Yoshimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.86,0:26:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.73,0:26:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. I'm Anthony from the Matenrou duo.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.13,0:26:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm full of dread.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.93,0:26:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.23,0:26:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I think his career is a lot shorter\Nthan the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.13,0:26:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If he doesn't hold back\Nin front of his seniors,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.73,0:26:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,he might do well...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.50,0:26:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Anthony?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.73,0:26:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he might hold back a little\Nout of respect for his seniors.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.20,0:27:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Last month I earned 220,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.40,0:27:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I borrowed 500,000 yen\Nfrom my senior colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.90,0:27:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, BKB.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.90,0:27:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to regret lending you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.20,0:27:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Make me glad that I lent it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.13,0:27:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-Certainly.\N-Keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.60,0:27:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm sure you have the money.\N-I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.96,0:27:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop acting poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.80,0:27:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for lending me the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.36,0:27:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I borrowed from my mom as well,\Nand I finally raised one million.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.13,0:27:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the only one not fully Japanese,\Nso it'll be interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.83,0:27:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But when it comes to these guys,\Nit's like what I said about Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.63,0:27:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't laugh at his usual jokes.\NNot when he only looks a bit different.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.23,0:27:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first got to quit my part-time job\Nafter becoming a comedian,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.53,0:27:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.93,0:27:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I never want to have\Na part-time job again.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.16,0:27:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I lose this,\NI'll have to find a part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.20,0:27:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like a backpacker.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.63,0:27:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd he come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.16,0:28:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-Stop making funny quips.\N-Why? We haven't started yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.96,0:28:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks like a hitchhiker.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.90,0:28:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So there are nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.63,0:28:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We have nine participants now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.56,0:28:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That means there's one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.16,0:28:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,One more.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.96,0:28:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is the last participant?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.86,0:28:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's someone from Yoshimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.40,0:28:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-No way.\N-The worst participant!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.40,0:28:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh, no!\N-This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.76,0:28:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Jimmy Onishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.33,0:28:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just going to try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.70,0:28:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.43,0:28:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The nine others are not going to like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.46,0:28:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Not with him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.56,0:28:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The consumer loan officer told me\NI can't borrow a million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.76,0:28:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Because my annual income is only\Nsix million.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.03,0:29:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It really hit me how low\Nmy standing is in society.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.36,0:29:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He laughs easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.80,0:29:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All it would take is one\Nreally simple dirty joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.50,0:29:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He's that stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.16,0:29:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.66,0:29:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumb luck always plays a part in comedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.80,0:29:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to aim for dumb luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.66,0:29:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already won.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.93,0:29:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how grey his hair is.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.16,0:29:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-Stop saying things like that.\N-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.16,0:29:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.43,0:29:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really going to be something.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.76,0:29:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They are quite an elite troop.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.60,0:30:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,THE ELITE TROOP
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.86,0:30:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this will be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.10,0:30:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.20,0:30:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-With him here...\N-Jimmy is too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.13,0:30:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be over before we use\Nany of our props.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.76,0:30:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you laughing because he's black?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.83,0:30:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.50,0:30:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.36,0:30:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.60,0:30:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.16,0:30:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks very angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.86,0:30:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-He's scary.\N-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.70,0:30:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-He's angry.\N-Why's he so mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.26,0:30:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at his muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.00,0:30:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He's nice and pumped now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.76,0:30:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He gets more buff every time I see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.70,0:30:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-Good morning.\N-Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.10,0:30:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So, gentlemen...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.60,0:30:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you bring it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.90,0:30:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-Have you brought what we promised?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.20,0:30:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Of course we did.\N-Then put it on the table, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.16,0:31:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is truly your own money, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.16,0:31:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-You all raised it somehow?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.23,0:31:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,One million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.06,0:31:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you're doing this to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.73,0:31:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.20,0:31:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Spending money is easy,\Nbut making it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.40,0:31:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. You are right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.86,0:31:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, that's worn!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.63,0:31:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,His is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.50,0:31:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Which country is this rubber band from?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.03,0:31:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who looks at things like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.16,0:31:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind passing the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.96,0:31:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Our staff will confirm\Nit's all there later.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.36,0:31:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sure there are no mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.96,0:31:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Please start from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.33,0:31:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.56,0:31:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-I just pass it around?\N-Yes, please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.50,0:31:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-The cameras are rolling.\N-You're not handing out homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.53,0:31:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-I've never done this before.\N-What a nice chunk of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.90,0:31:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-I can't believe we are doing this.\N-It looks beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.63,0:32:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how tall the pile gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.63,0:32:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-I've never seen 10 million yen before.\N-It's huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.16,0:32:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yeah, now that you mention it.\N-Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.50,0:32:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.26,0:32:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wow!\N-Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.26,0:32:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.56,0:32:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?\NHe's trying to make you laugh already?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.90,0:32:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.93,0:32:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,DAISUKE & HANAKO\N"TOGETHER FOR 35 YEARS"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.46,0:32:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a joke. It's a good luck charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.66,0:32:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's more like a bad luck charm.\N-It's their 35th wedding anniversary.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.56,0:32:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's a bad luck charm.\N-No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.96,0:32:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-Stop saying they're bad luck.\N-That veteran duo isn't "bad luck."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.76,0:32:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop making pointless jokes.\NThey're irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.36,0:32:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So, here is the money you brought.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.50,0:32:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nine million yen here.\NI mean 10 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.96,0:32:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The 10 million yen is in this bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.80,0:32:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.90,0:32:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to explain the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.60,0:32:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Rule 2:\NThere are 10 participants in this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.10,0:32:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You will spend the entire time together\Nconfined in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.83,0:33:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rule 3: At the end, the person who hasn't\Nlaughed will receive the reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.36,0:33:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,10 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.86,0:33:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Rule 4: There is a time limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.60,0:33:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It is displayed up there.\NYou have six hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.83,0:33:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as I call start,\Nit will begin counting down.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.13,0:33:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Before the six hours are up,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.86,0:33:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to see one of you become\Nthe champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.50,0:33:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.70,0:33:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-You can do whatever you want.\N-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.16,0:33:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do absolutely anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.33,0:33:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The funniest person wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.70,0:33:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it. This is an amazing event.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.86,0:33:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We simply have to be funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.26,0:33:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's worth being a champion here.\N-Yes, winning here will be like...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.40,0:33:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It could mean even more than\Nwinning the M-1 Grand Prix.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.03,0:33:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's not a comedy sketch.\N-We're fighting with our bare fists.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.66,0:33:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Things like, "The mechanism of laughter."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.90,0:33:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And, "What is laughter?"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.00,0:33:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"What is it that we find truly funny?"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.23,0:34:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this program will make us consider
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.66,0:34:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,concepts like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.33,0:34:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I still haven't found answers\Nto questions like that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.30,0:34:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get your one million yen,\NAnthony?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.76,0:34:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I borrowed it from many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.90,0:34:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Anthony has a lot more work recently,\Nbut a million yen is still a big amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.80,0:34:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked Akebono, the sumo wrestler,\Nfor a loan.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.53,0:34:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, "No damn way."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.33,0:34:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you ask him?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.26,0:34:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Akebono, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.16,0:34:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-But a million's nothing for Jimmy, right?\N-That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.76,0:34:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to loan companies,\Nlike Promise and Acom,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.53,0:34:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but they said, with my income,\Nthey can't loan me one million.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.96,0:34:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.26,0:34:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-But your paintings are popular.\N-You could sell one.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.90,0:34:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on a break from painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.73,0:34:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What does he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.76,0:34:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,At the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.50,0:34:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,he's more interested in sex than painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.40,0:35:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-My sex drive's winning at the moment.\N-Your art is losing?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.53,0:35:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-And now...\N-How old is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.30,0:35:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-Nowadays, I stop.\N-Stop what?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.80,0:35:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm about to cum.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.40,0:35:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm about to cum, I stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.60,0:35:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.30,0:35:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-Why do you stop?\N-We're done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.00,0:35:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-Why not just cum?\N-The time's too expensive to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.73,0:35:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-What time?\N-I pay for two whole hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.43,0:35:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-Are you talking about sex clubs?\N-Yeah, at the sex club.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.13,0:35:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,At the sex club?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.86,0:35:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He's doing it himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.10,0:35:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Jimmy's not the best storyteller.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.83,0:35:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's difficult to understand,\Nbut please make an effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.70,0:35:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So, at the loan company, they said,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.53,0:35:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"With your income,\Nwe can't loan you one million yen."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.46,0:35:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Really?\N-Is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.46,0:35:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He is my only senior colleague here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.90,0:35:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior by a few months?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.06,0:35:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A few months... Two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.30,0:35:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's funny about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.30,0:35:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So, gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.80,0:35:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you have a kitchen there,\Nif you ever feel hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.83,0:35:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not here to see you\Nbattle with hunger.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.73,0:36:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There's alcohol and such\Nin the refrigerator,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.33,0:36:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,if you would like to drink some.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.03,0:36:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The staff will not come in at all.\NIf something comes up, ring me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.96,0:36:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,RULE 5:\NMATSUMOTO MAY CALL TO GIVE ORDERS, TOO
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.86,0:36:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how things will go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.60,0:36:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-You have six hours to find one winner.\N-We won't need six hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.40,0:36:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. You won't need six hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.23,0:36:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-No, we don't need six hours, do we?\N-No, we don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.40,0:36:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, you can do whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.10,0:36:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly, you can do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.50,0:36:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is off limits for broadcast?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.80,0:36:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-There must be some limits.\N-Apparently not.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.76,0:36:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You say we're free, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.20,0:36:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You have six hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.13,0:36:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-It may seem long, or the time may fly.\N-I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.93,0:36:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,For the next six hours,\Ngood luck to you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.76,0:36:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is scary now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.13,0:36:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-When do we start?\N-Will they tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.03,0:36:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I will let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.03,0:36:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Smile and relax until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.80,0:36:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Jimmy, please wipe off\Nyour eye mucus first.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.70,0:36:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.10,0:37:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Eye mucus first.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.80,0:37:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He is getting older.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.10,0:37:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-You're clear.\N-He's at that age when you get eye mucus.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.23,0:37:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with all this, look at these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.03,0:37:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Kawahara and Jiro haven't laughed at all.\N-You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.93,0:37:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's not fair.\N-They don't talk either.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.80,0:37:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-They're tough.\N-No, they're just missing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.50,0:37:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-They forgot how to feel.\N-They're missing something inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.63,0:37:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are you guys ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.16,0:37:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Documental,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.00,0:37:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,start!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.83,0:37:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go. The game has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.70,0:37:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,May the best player win.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.10,0:37:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my first time meeting Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.50,0:37:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm Jiro Hachimitsu, from Tokyo Dynamite.\N-I'm a great fan of your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.43,0:37:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.36,0:37:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-Do you have something to say?\N-It's my first time as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.36,0:37:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to meet you.\NI'm Kyojin, from All Hanshin.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.33,0:37:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-No, you're not.\N-He's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.90,0:37:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.60,0:37:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-Which of the duo are you?\N-Kyojin.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.36,0:38:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Jimmy?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.70,0:38:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-You're Kyojin?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.23,0:38:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-You're not Hanshin?\N-But you're short.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.26,0:38:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Jimmy is very close.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.83,0:38:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyojin is the tall one.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.53,0:38:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Jimmy...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.10,0:38:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Jimmy?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.93,0:38:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. I'm going to stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.30,0:38:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I go outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.70,0:38:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.20,0:38:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.13,0:38:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Who's out?\N-Don't joke like that from the very start.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.16,0:38:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is it you?\N-No, I laughed after the buzzer.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.40,0:38:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,RULE 6: LAUGHTER IS PERMITTED\NWHILE PLAY IS SUSPENDED
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.00,0:38:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-Who was it?\N-Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.70,0:38:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wait.\N-Who laughed first?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.36,0:38:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi, I can't believe you did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.83,0:38:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty much everyone laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.36,0:38:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is really...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.90,0:38:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I will let this one go,\Nbut almost everyone was laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.10,0:38:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-You consider that laughing?\N-This is going to be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.90,0:38:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost everyone laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.30,0:38:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-Where does a "laugh" start?\N-You can't have your mouth open wide.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.50,0:38:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-Okay?\N-Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.13,0:38:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-You all laughed.\N-Jimmy, that's too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.76,0:39:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-Am I the best so far?\N-You were really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.00,0:39:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's just the beginning.\NCan't we slowly ease into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.36,0:39:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-No.\N-We can't. We started.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.30,0:39:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. Only 18 seconds have passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.20,0:39:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-That was quick.\N-Jimmy, that was way too quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.83,0:39:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to stop this.\NCan you stop the timer for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.16,0:39:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-I didn't want to stop.\N-This is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.06,0:39:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.83,0:39:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone was laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.26,0:39:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make it clear.\NWe have to keep a normal, natural face.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.96,0:39:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's right.\N-Otherwise--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.53,0:39:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's check what our normal\Nfaces look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.53,0:39:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,To be precise, Jiro was laughing a bit\Nwhen he introduced himself to Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.80,0:39:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,RULE 7:\NSMILING WILL BE RULED AS A LAUGH
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.20,0:39:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-He smiled.\N-We can't even smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.03,0:39:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.16,0:39:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we have to see everyone's\Nnormal face first.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.93,0:39:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.50,0:39:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to.\NWhy do you want to see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.73,0:39:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get any more chances!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.96,0:39:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-We're not the judges.\N-No more chances!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.03,0:39:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimoto, stop coming in so fast.\NYou're relentless.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.73,0:39:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He's killing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.66,0:40:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm serious.\N-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.60,0:40:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my normal face.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.36,0:40:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my normal face, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.43,0:40:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's your normal face.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.53,0:40:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.96,0:40:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But Fujimoto's face is kind of smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.00,0:40:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Put on a more neutral face.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.40,0:40:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-Like that.\N-I have to stay like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.73,0:40:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-That will do.\N-This is going to be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.06,0:40:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you guys gave me no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.80,0:40:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone was all smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.26,0:40:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we'll be done in about 18 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.80,0:40:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll finish really quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.16,0:40:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-We won't last that long.\N-It's no fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.26,0:40:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Jimmy, that face is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.03,0:40:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-Like this?\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.30,0:40:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep that face.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.93,0:40:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.20,0:40:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making us laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.96,0:40:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm allowed to laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.20,0:40:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.93,0:40:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-Don't attack us from the side.\N-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.63,0:40:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.63,0:40:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're about to start.\NLet's put on neutral faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.36,0:40:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep a neutral face.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.20,0:40:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Jimmy, you're smiling.\N-I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.06,0:40:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.30,0:40:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Daisuke, stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.76,0:40:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.96,0:41:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Play's still suspended, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.53,0:41:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my normal face.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.56,0:41:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-You're smiling.\N-I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.93,0:41:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You are smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.06,0:41:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You are smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.70,0:41:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.33,0:41:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-You call this smiling?\N-Yes. You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.43,0:41:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You are. Look at your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.83,0:41:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-Your nose is laughing.\N-I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.26,0:41:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go. Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.13,0:41:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I blow my nose too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.63,0:41:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-Should we put our things in a locker?\N-You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.46,0:41:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he blows his nose too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.83,0:41:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-Where are the lockers?\N-In the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.90,0:41:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,THE ROOM COMES WITH A BATH,\NSHOWER AND TOILET
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.16,0:41:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawahara looks dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.76,0:41:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-I didn't know we could smoke here.\N-You can have some of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.96,0:41:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Put that envelope away.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.50,0:41:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh, sorry.\N-Give it to Fujimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.70,0:41:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.96,0:41:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.96,0:41:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Fujimoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.86,0:41:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the lockers?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.03,0:42:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimoto has sort of been smirking.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.73,0:42:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-We have sushi, too.\N-Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.60,0:42:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.66,0:42:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-He can make us sushi.\N-Lucky us.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.56,0:42:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make some later.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.36,0:42:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want any of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.40,0:42:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-I don't know about your sushi.\N-But my parents own a sushi restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.33,0:42:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Put those envelopes away.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.00,0:42:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he roaming around?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.30,0:42:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-Where did you get the envelopes?\N-I bought them.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.33,0:42:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You stole the envelopes from\NDaisuke & Hanako's dressing room?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.53,0:42:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I stole from them?\NWhat would they have to steal?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.46,0:42:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm sure there's something.\N-They have nothing but great jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.96,0:42:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What a square.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.03,0:42:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-Stop fighting.\N-We're not here to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.70,0:42:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.30,0:42:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take turns at smoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.90,0:42:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Jimmy's making a move already.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.60,0:42:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This set is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.56,0:43:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimoto looks suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.40,0:43:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a nice kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.93,0:43:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.66,0:43:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-We can go over here, right?\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.53,0:43:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-We can spread out.\N-Anything goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.63,0:43:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.43,0:43:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You brought heaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.60,0:43:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is that wine?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.20,0:43:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-Drinking already?\N-From the bottle?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.50,0:43:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-You're cool.\N-I'm going to drink wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.46,0:43:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like Julie's song.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.46,0:43:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want some nibbles?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.13,0:43:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want something to nibble?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.26,0:43:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-No, thanks.\N-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.53,0:43:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No nibbles or giggles?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.80,0:43:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-Stop it.\N-He's like a bartender.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.40,0:43:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,At a bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.43,0:43:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's hot in here.\N-This is a nice frying pan.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.06,0:43:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the shower this way? Oh, it's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.53,0:43:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.73,0:43:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They brought one in.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.70,0:44:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop roaming around, Anthony.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.76,0:44:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in my line of sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.56,0:44:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.70,0:44:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-We still have a long way to go.\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.23,0:44:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-It hasn't even been 10 minutes.\N-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.10,0:44:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-We have six hours here.\N-Those 10 minutes went by quickly for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.76,0:44:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.10,0:44:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's faster than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.53,0:44:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-10 minutes have passed already?\N-Not yet. It's been six.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.90,0:44:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only been six minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.46,0:44:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.00,0:44:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-Are we allowed to smoke?\N-You can smoke over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.63,0:44:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, wherever.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.06,0:44:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is that really alcohol?\N-It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.23,0:44:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's red wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.40,0:44:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-Red wine.\N-Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.00,0:44:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd rather be drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.56,0:44:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I just like alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.76,0:44:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-Were you born in Spain?\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.66,0:44:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This polo shirt is from Spain.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.96,0:45:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the exact same shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.06,0:45:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But I bought mine in Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.96,0:45:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-As a present on a holiday.\N-I got mine at the mall.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.66,0:45:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought it on a family trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.00,0:45:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,At the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.40,0:45:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The hotel's boutique.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.63,0:45:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't ask about your shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.93,0:45:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have this shirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.10,0:45:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw a homeless guy wearing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.46,0:45:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The old guy had the very same one.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.90,0:45:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The polo shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.13,0:45:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We all bought one.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.50,0:45:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So, my wife has one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.40,0:45:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She has the dress version.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.00,0:45:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-She has the dress version.\N-Who does?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.06,0:45:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-We all decided to buy the same one.\N-Your wife, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.50,0:45:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean your giant wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.53,0:46:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like she's Giant Shirota.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.20,0:46:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not Giant Shirota.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.96,0:46:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My "giant wife"?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.23,0:46:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not Giant Shirota!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.73,0:46:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This tastes great.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.93,0:46:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohchi is very close. And here's Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.20,0:46:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They're mother and child.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.40,0:46:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.40,0:46:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohchi laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.46,0:46:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.80,0:46:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Who laughed?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.76,0:46:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.30,0:46:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-Was it Jimmy?\N-It's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.53,0:46:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-Seriously, who was it?\N-Not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.06,0:46:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-Who was it?\N-Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.23,0:47:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Phew!\N-He's been laughing for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.36,0:47:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-He was laughing a fair bit.\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.30,0:47:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd actually been chuckling\Nfor quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.26,0:47:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He was soft on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.46,0:47:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-What happened?\N-He was laughing the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.16,0:47:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.00,0:47:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-We can laugh now, right?\N-It's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.06,0:47:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You laughed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.33,0:47:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You were chuckling, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.73,0:47:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Because everyone was funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.63,0:47:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't said anything funny yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.56,0:47:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It was nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.76,0:47:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are wandering around too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.90,0:47:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-To muster up the courage.\N-I want you to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.96,0:47:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too early for things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.00,0:47:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He set me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.43,0:47:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too early to set us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.40,0:47:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-What are they?\N-They're mother and child.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.36,0:47:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mother and child.\N-Are you still going?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.80,0:47:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-So what if they're mother and child?\N-She was hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.53,0:47:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.86,0:47:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.93,0:47:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to watch a replay,\Njust to confirm that Ohchi laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.73,0:48:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you know already,\Nbut we'll play it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.06,0:48:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We have video evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.46,0:48:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He was so quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.50,0:48:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's watch the replay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.26,0:48:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not hide our laughter with\Ncigarettes or drinks, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.16,0:48:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks like Al Capone.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.03,0:48:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Al Capone.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.93,0:48:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Yoshimoto's Al Capone.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.56,0:48:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The cigarette tasted good.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.86,0:48:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You were laughing a lot before this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.96,0:48:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.36,0:48:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you get a yellow card.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.83,0:48:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You only get a yellow card for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.00,0:48:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Look.\N-He's laughing hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.63,0:48:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.63,0:48:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We've really only just started.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.40,0:48:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm safe. But if I get a red card?\N-You're out.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.33,0:48:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If he laughs at something like that,\Nhe'll be out in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.10,0:48:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-You'd better start getting serious.\N-Yes. Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.93,0:48:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-I got it.\N-It's one million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.66,0:48:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I definitely won't laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.43,0:48:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.73,0:49:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell was that?
